    <section class="inner-service sec-pd">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="service-heading text-center mb-5">
                    <h2 class="sec-hd color-green" data-aos="zoom-out" data-aos-duration="900"
                        data-aos-easing="ease-out-cubic" data-aos-delay="0">Effective Book Marketing Services to Boost
                        Visibility</h2>
                    <p class="w-85 mx-auto" data-aos="zoom-out" data-aos-duration="1000"
                        data-aos-easing="ease-out-cubic" data-aos-delay="200">At United Book Publishing, we help authors
                        connect with the right readers, grow sales, and expand their audience. Our book marketing
                        services combine strategy, creativity, and practical execution to make your book stand out.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                    <div class="market-box" data-aos="flip-left" data-aos-easing="ease-out-cubic"
                        data-aos-duration="1500" data-aos-delay="0">
                        <div class="market-icon text-end">
                            <img src="assets/img/market-icon1.webp" class="img-fluid" alt="Media Coverage">
                        </div>
                        <div class="market-content">
                            <h3 class="color fw-500">Target Audience Analysis</h3>
                            <p class="mb-0">Understanding your readers is key. We study demographics, interests, and
                                reading habits to identify the perfect audience. This insight allows us to create
                                campaigns that truly resonate and convert readers into loyal fans.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                    <div class="market-box mid" data-aos="flip-right" data-aos-easing="ease-out-cubic"
                        data-aos-duration="1500" data-aos-delay="200">
                        <div class="market-icon text-end">
                            <img src="assets/img/market-icon3.webp" class="img-fluid" alt="Amazon Bestseller">
                        </div>
                        <div class="market-content">
                            <h3 class="color fw-500">Strategic Campaign Planning</h3>
                            <p class="mb-0">Clear strategy drives effective results. We plan structured campaigns across
                                blogs, newsletters, social media, and multimedia to build engagement and strengthen your
                                author presence. Every step is designed to create consistent visibility and lasting impact.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                    <div class="market-box" data-aos="flip-left" data-aos-easing="ease-out-cubic"
                        data-aos-duration="1500" data-aos-delay="400">
                        <div class="market-icon text-end">
                            <img src="assets/img/market-icon3.webp" class="img-fluid" alt="Online Presence">
                        </div>
                        <div class="market-content">
                            <h3 class="color fw-500">Content Marketing</h3>
                            <p class="mb-0">Engaging content drives reader interest and builds your author brand.
                                Through blog posts, social media updates, newsletters, and multimedia campaigns, our
                                book marketing services create meaningful connections with your audience. Compelling
                                content encourages sharing, boosts visibility, and positions your work as a must-read in
                                its genre.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                    <div class="market-box" data-aos="flip-left" data-aos-easing="ease-out-cubic"
                        data-aos-duration="1500" data-aos-delay="600">
                        <div class="market-icon text-end">
                            <img src="assets/img/market-icon4.webp" class="img-fluid" alt="Content Publication">
                        </div>
                        <div class="market-content">
                            <h3 class="color fw-500">Book Launch Promotion</h3>
                            <p class="mb-0">A strong launch sets the tone for your book’s success. We create buzz
                                through pre-launch campaigns, social media teasers, and targeted outreach. With our book
                                marketing services for self-published authors, your launch attracts attention, generates
                                reviews, and engages readers from day one.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                    <div class="market-box mid" data-aos="flip-right" data-aos-easing="ease-out-cubic"
                        data-aos-duration="1500" data-aos-delay="800">
                        <div class="market-icon text-end">
                            <img src="assets/img/market-icon5.webp" class="img-fluid" alt="Paid Promotions">
                        </div>
                        <div class="market-content">
                            <h3 class="color fw-500">Online Presence Building</h3>
                            <p class="mb-0">A professional online footprint is essential. Hence, when it comes to
                                building an online presence for authors, we strive for maximum channels and mediums relevant
                                to your genre and audience. Online presence building includes optimizing websites, creating
                                author profiles, and listings to make you and your book easy to find and highly visible.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                    <div class="market-box" data-aos="flip-left" data-aos-easing="ease-out-cubic"
                        data-aos-duration="1500" data-aos-delay="1000">
                        <div class="market-icon text-end">
                            <img src="assets/img/market-icon6.webp" class="img-fluid" alt="Long Term RoadMap">
                        </div>
                        <div class="market-content">
                            <h3 class="color fw-500">Reviews and Influencer Outreach</h3>
                            <p class="mb-0">Positive reviews and trusted influencer endorsements strengthen your book’s
                                credibility and expand its reach. We identify relevant reviewers, bloggers, and social media
                                influencers, #BookTok community, then manage outreach and campaign coordination to showcase
                                your work effectively. Our affordable book marketing services help your book gain momentum
                                and connect with wider, highly targeted audiences.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>


            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

