    <section class="process-tab-sec sec-pd">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="process-heading text-center mb-5">
                    <div class="font-35 let-space theme-font color-green fw-600" data-aos="zoom-out"
                        data-aos-duration="900" data-aos-easing="ease-out-cubic" data-aos-delay="0">Our proven </div>
                    <h2 class="sec-hd color" data-aos="zoom-out" data-aos-duration="1000"
                        data-aos-easing="ease-out-cubic" data-aos-delay="200">Book Marketing Process For Max Output</h2>
                    <p class="w-80 mx-auto mb-0" data-aos="zoom-out" data-aos-duration="1100"
                        data-aos-easing="ease-out-cubic" data-aos-delay="400">Marketing a book is more than promotion,
                        it’s about connecting with the right readers. We guide authors through every step, from
                        understanding their audience to creating campaigns that build engagement, awareness, and lasting
                        visibility</p>
                </div>

                <div class="process-slider-sec">
                    <div class="process-for mb-5">

                        <div class="process-content-box">
                            <div class="row align-items-center">
                                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-5">
                                    <div class="phase-img">
                                        <img src="assets/img/our-story.png" class="img-fluid" alt="img">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12">
                                    <div class="process-content">
                                        <h2>Discovery Positioning</h2>
                                        <p>Effective book marketing services begin with understanding your audience, genre,
                                            and goals. This stage focuses on positioning your book clearly within the
                                            market. Identifying reader expectations helps shape messaging and direction. A
                                            strong foundation ensures your book stands out among similar titles. With proper
                                            positioning, your marketing efforts become more focused and effective. This step
                                            creates clarity, allowing your book to connect with the right readers from the
                                            start.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="process-content-box">
                            <div class="row align-items-center">
                                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-5">
                                    <div class="phase-img">
                                        <img src="assets/img/web-bann.webp" class="img-fluid" alt="img">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12">
                                    <div class="process-content">
                                        <h2>Audience Market Analysis</h2>
                                        <p>Understanding your audience is essential for effective marketing. A clear
                                            analysis identifies reader interests, behavior, and preferences. It helps
                                            position your book in the right category and reach the right people. By studying
                                            trends, genres, and engagement patterns, marketing efforts become more focused.
                                            This process reduces guesswork and improves results. With proper audience
                                            insight, your messaging becomes stronger, your campaigns perform better, and
                                            your book connects with readers who are more likely to engage and respond.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="process-content-box">
                            <div class="row align-items-center">
                                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-5">
                                    <div class="phase-img">
                                        <img src="assets/img/book-cover-design.png" class="img-fluid" alt="img">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12">
                                    <div class="process-content">
                                        <h2>Marketing Strategy Campaign Planning</h2>
                                        <p>A structured book marketing plan ensures every action has purpose and direction.
                                            This stage focuses on defining channels, timelines, and campaign goals. Planning
                                            helps avoid random efforts and creates consistency. Each campaign is customized
                                            to your book’s genre and audience. With a clear strategy, your marketing becomes
                                            more effective and measurable. This step ensures your efforts are aligned,
                                            helping your book gain visibility and build momentum over time.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="process-content-box">
                            <div class="row align-items-center">
                                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-5">
                                    <div class="phase-img">
                                        <img src="assets/img/ghost-b.webp" class="img-fluid" alt="img">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12">
                                    <div class="process-content">
                                        <h2>Platform Asset Preparation</h2>
                                        <p>Preparing the right assets is essential for success. With affordable book
                                            marketing services, authors can develop visuals, descriptions, and promotional
                                            materials that attract attention. This stage ensures your book is presented
                                            professionally across platforms. Strong assets improve engagement and encourage
                                            readers to take action. From graphics to content, everything is designed to
                                            support your marketing goals. Proper preparation ensures your campaigns perform
                                            effectively and deliver consistent results.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="process-content-box">
                            <div class="row align-items-center">
                                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-5">
                                    <div class="phase-img">
                                        <img src="assets/img/about-bann.webp" class="img-fluid" alt="img">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12">
                                    <div class="process-content">
                                        <h2>Campaign Execution Growth</h2>
                                        <p>Executing campaigns with online book marketing services ensures your book reaches
                                            readers through the right channels. This stage focuses on launching promotions,
                                            engaging audiences, and building visibility. Consistent effort helps create
                                            awareness and encourages interaction. Campaigns are monitored to maintain
                                            performance and adjust strategies when needed. Effective execution ensures your
                                            book gains traction and continues to grow its presence across platforms where
                                            readers actively engage.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="process-content-box">
                            <div class="row align-items-center">
                                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-5">
                                    <div class="phase-img">
                                        <img src="assets/img/make-book.webp" class="img-fluid" alt="img">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12">
                                    <div class="process-content">
                                        <h2>Performance Tracking Optimization</h2>
                                        <p>Tracking results helps refine your approach and improve outcomes. Using social
                                            media marketing books insights, campaigns are evaluated for engagement and
                                            reach. Data helps identify what works and what needs adjustment. Continuous
                                            optimization ensures your efforts remain effective. This stage focuses on
                                            improving performance over time, helping your book reach more readers and
                                            maintain visibility. With consistent tracking, your marketing becomes more
                                            strategic and impactful.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="process-nav text-center">
                        <div class="phase-box">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-lightbulb font-40 mb-3"></i>
                            <p class="font-15 fw-500">Discovery <br> Positioning</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="phase-box">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-gear font-40 mb-3"></i>
                            <p class="font-15 fw-500">Audience <br>Market Analysis</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="phase-box">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-users font-40 mb-3"></i>
                            <p class="font-15 fw-500">Marketing Strategy <br>Campaign Planning</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="phase-box">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-comment-dots font-40 mb-3"></i>
                            <p class="font-15 fw-500">Platform <br> Asset Preparation</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="phase-box">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-share-nodes font-40 mb-3"></i>
                            <p class="font-15 fw-500">Campaign Execution <br> Growth</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="phase-box">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-comment-dots font-40 mb-3"></i>
