                    <div class="font-35 let-space theme-font color-green fw-600" data-aos="zoom-out"
                        data-aos-duration="900" data-aos-easing="ease-out-cubic" data-aos-delay="0">More Than a
                        Publisher</div>

                    <!-- Main Heading -->
                    <h2 class="sec-hd color mb-0" data-aos="zoom-out" data-aos-duration="1000"
                        data-aos-easing="ease-out-cubic" data-aos-delay="200">
                        We Believe Your Story is a Legacy Waiting to be Told!
                    </h2>

                    <!-- Paragraph -->
                    <p class="w-80 mx-auto mb-0" data-aos="zoom-out" data-aos-duration="1100"
                        data-aos-easing="ease-out-cubic" data-aos-delay="400">In a world with thousands of book
                        publishing companies in the States, we offer a different path. Our integrated book editing and
                        publishing services are designed to guide authors from manuscripts to finished books seamlessly.
                        No shortcuts. No generic writing. Just thoughtful collaboration that turns your ideas into a
