                <div class="choose-heading text-center mb-5">
                    <div class="font-35 let-space theme-font color-green fw-600" data-aos="zoom-out"
                        data-aos-duration="900" data-aos-easing="ease-out-cubic" data-aos-delay="0">FREQUENTLY ASKED
                        QUESTIONS</div>
                    <h2 class="sec-hd color mb-0" data-aos="zoom-out" data-aos-duration="1000"
                        data-aos-easing="ease-out-cubic" data-aos-delay="200">Common Questions About Book Publishing</h2>
                    <p class="w-80 mx-auto mb-0" data-aos="zoom-out" data-aos-duration="1100"
                        data-aos-easing="ease-out-cubic" data-aos-delay="400">Your book deserves to be found. Book
                        marketing services should connect you with readers who will love your work. Let us build a campaign
                        that turns curiosity into sales.</p>
                </div>



                <div class="col-lg-6">
